	   <tr><td colspan=2>The plane of Air is incredibly hard.&nbsp;&nbsp;Completing this quest would require at least a week in Air with a very large raiding party.  And usually, it takes multiple trips to Air to complete quests on these far islands.  If you have that much firepower, there are a lot better weapons you can get for a lot less effort.<br><br>To put things in perspective, I wield a gnarled staff and a phenocryst.  Combined they give me:<br>25 int, 15 hps, 85 mana, 23 sv cold, 30 sv magic, 3 sv fire, poison & disease, 3 dex, 3 cha, 5 ac.  That is a ton better than the Nargon staff - and both items were a heck of a lot easier to get.  No wizard who is strong enough to get this staff would actually use it.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
